title: Bella Hadid Reveals Her Inner Kate Moss in This NSFW Magazine Shoot
text:
Visit the original post to see all 7 images from this gallery. 
What can go wrong when you mix Bella Hadid with some classic Kate Moss vibes? The correct and obvious answer is absolutely nothing at all.
In a new editorial for V magazine, the supermodel (nearly) bears all and frees the nipple in a shoot that pastiches Kate’s classic 1993 ad campaign for Calvin Klein’s Obsession fragrance. Shot in black and white, Bella can be seen striking a selection of sultry poses, while casting alluring glances at the camera. Forgive us for being obsessed, pardon the pun.
Head over to the V website to pre-order issue 106 before it hits stands on March 9.
In related news, Elizabeth Elam covers the March 2017 issue of Playboy.
